# Pin bundled dataset files to LF line endings.
#
# The dataset registry hash (data/datasets.yaml) is computed over each document's
# byte content. With git's autocrlf enabled, a Windows checkout rewrites these
# files to CRLF, changing their hashes and breaking `dataset validate` /
# `benchmark run --dataset sample@<version>` with a "Dataset hash mismatch". See
# issue #39. Forcing LF keeps the on-disk bytes identical across platforms.
* text eol=lf
